{
  "stem": "833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had no recourse to any legal authority, to the police, to even a lawyer-- to nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were just exposed to a complete bunch of ruffians who took charge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I see the next morning, you have the son of our concierge, down there-- the housekeeper, what we call it here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came up, the son, and said to my brother, the key!",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother said, what, the key?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, the key of your car!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's mine now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother says, what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he made like this, and we saw that he had a-- he had  a gun here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother gave him the key.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And people could-- could stop you on the street, kill you, then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody would look-- look away from it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, I mean-- And now we must not forget that 80%, let's say, of the law profession was in Jewish hands.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were 186 full-time journalists in Vienna, at the various newspapers, which is a large number, of which 176 were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, I mean, the Jewish penetration of the culture, of the intellectual life, of the-- of the professional life, was so strong that that also created, of course, that anti-Semitism about those who did not achieve that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "See, what anti-Semitism creates is that, since Jews were not allowed to apply to acquire property for centuries, they had to find another way to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The only way just to live by their wits.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So to sharpen their wits was a thing that, in babyhood, you had to start.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's why they could be good as mathematicians, as writers, as what-- any kind-- which-- which you could take with yourself is Semite.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
